8.3 Design Refinements for Multi-Leg Integration and Flight Readiness

· Redundancy and Fault Tolerance: Incorporate dual independent pressure sensors with voting logic for bellows leak detection. Use a passive constant-force spring as a mechanical fallback for biarticular tendon tension.
